cs.LO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.MA

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with temporal logic specifications and their control for dynamical systems. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper focuses on stochastic linear dynamics and control strategies. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes an algorithm for synthesizing control strategies to ensure temporal logic specifications are satisfied. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper uses abstraction-refinement techniques, which are commonly used in program verification and synthesis. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with turn-based 2-player probabilistic games, which can be used to model multiagent systems.
